Kuryamira urubavu rw’iburyo (ni byiza nk’impalternativa)
 Impamvu: nta kibazo gikomeye, ariko urubavu rw’ibumoso ruba rufite inyungu nyinshi;
gusimburanya impande zombi birinda kubabara mu mugongo no

 Ntukoreshe amavuta cyangwa ikindi kintu kirimo amavuta kuko amavuta ahembera ubushyuhe
mu gihe wowe ushaka kubugabanya ;
 Ntumukuremo umwenda yahiye yambaye ugafatira ku bushye kuko byatuma igikomer

